Android demo OAuth Client


To open with Android Studio use "Import project (Eclipse ADT, Gradle, etc.)" in Quick Start and select
the oauthclient path.

Configuration is defined under Config class in AuthActivity.java

Config.useTokenInfo selects the sequence to be used:
useTokenInfo = true -> implement the mobile app & resource server sequence and use tokeninfo
useTokenInfo = false -> implement the web app sequence and use userinfo

Misc notes:

SSL certificate check is disabled.